    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a champ. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure! It runs like a dream and is perfect for everything from daily commutes to weekend road trips. I've loved driving this car, and I know you will too. Come take it for a spin and see why I'm so excited about it!",
